104
00:13:31,168 --> 00:13:34,668
I am reaching, but I fall>>

105
00:13:35,568 --> 00:13:38,768
And the night is closing in>>

106
00:13:39,368 --> 00:13:43,668
And I stare into the void>>

107
00:13:43,868 --> 00:13:47,668
